Subject: Re: [VB] Re: Hard shifting continues...

Your shift coupler is a later one, I would remove it and replace it with the
correct kind.  The correct kind looks like this:
http://www.thesamba.com/vw/forum/album_page.php?pic_id=342581

You will have issues from the clutch cable tube having broken loose.
I am not sure the zip ties are enough, but  did it make a difference?
Metal hose clamps, really big ones like from the axle boot kits, have worked
IME.



